Package com.documentum.fc.client.content

Interface IDfExternalStore

All Superinterfaces:
IDfPersistentObject, IDfStore, IDfTypedObject
All Known Subinterfaces:
IDfExternalFileStore
public interface IDfExternalStore extends IDfStore
An external content storage area for objects accessible to the server but whose physical contents are stored outside the server.
Since:
5.4
